Comment: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Comment: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:18.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
