Comment: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:29.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}溢る力が　不意に嗤い出した
Comment: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:35.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Comment: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Comment: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:45.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Comment: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}理解らない　構わない
Comment: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:50.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}紛い力振るっても
Comment: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:55.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜けよ
Comment: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:00.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}嗚呼　失くした哀しみがまた疼いてく…
